{"word":"ἐπανάγω","slug":"ἐπανάγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐπανάγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐπί\">ἐπί</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνάγω\">ἀνάγω</a></el>; ‘lead, bring up’] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a> ‘make one’s way to a destination’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on moving from a position, <b>go out,</b> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπὸ\">ἀπὸ</a> τῆς γῆς ἐ. ὀλίγον</el> push off a little from shore <b><a href='B:490 5:3'>Lk 5:3</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on reverting to a position, <b>return <a href='B:470 21:18'>Mt 21:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπάναγκες\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐπαναμιμνῄσκω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}